data.description: The Village of South Holland was named as the "Most Livable Metro-Area Suburb" of Chicago. This split-level home located close to eateries, shopping, and e-ways. It has 3 ample sized bedrooms with a shared primary bathroom. There are 2 half baths. Hardwood floors, Formal Dining Room, Eat-in Kitchen, Family Room, and Attached garage with additional front parking. Appliances stay. In addition, there is ample storage in a large 5ft crawl space. Newer thermos windows, furnace 2022, water heater 2021. South Holland's motto is "Clean Bright and Beautiful!"
